item.wizardrygolems\:ring_glistering.desc=Earth Golemancy always summons a Melon Golem which heals its owner during combat

item.wizardrygolems\:ring_forest_guardian.name=Ring of Forest Guardians
item.wizardrygolems\:ring_forest_guardian.desc=Earth Golemancy summons 2 Log Golems and 4 Leaf Golems

item.wizardrygolems\:charm_dried_mushroom.name=Dried Mushroom Charm
item.wizardrygolems\:charm_dried_mushroom.desc=Earth Golemancy summons 3 Mushroom Golems with poisonous attacks. Each golem has 50%% chance to spawn magical mushrooms upon death

item.wizardrygolems\:amulet_raging_skies.name=Amulet of Raging Skies
item.wizardrygolems\:amulet_raging_skies.desc=When a Lightning Golem dies, a lightning bolt emerges from the sky

item.wizardrygolems\:amulet_snare.name=Amulet of Brambles
item.wizardrygolems\:amulet_snare.desc=Earth Golemancy golems leave 1-5 Snare traps behind if killed

item.wizardrygolems\:amulet_deathweed.name=Deathweed Flower Amulet
item.wizardrygolems\:amulet_deathweed.desc=10%% chance to activate Forest's Curse when an Earth Golemancy golem is killed (100%% chance in forests)

# FIRE
item.wizardrygolems\:amulet_steaming_netherrack.name=Steaming Netherrack Amulet
item.wizardrygolems\:amulet_steaming_netherrack.desc=Golems summoned by Fire Golemancy will explode when killed

item.wizardrygolems\:ring_smoldering.name=Smoldering Ring
item.wizardrygolems\:ring_smoldering.desc=Fire Golemancy will summon a Magma Golem which can split into two when killed

item.wizardrygolems\:ring_flame_trail.name=Ring of Flame Trail
item.wizardrygolems\:ring_flame_trail.desc=Fire Golemancy minions set the ground under them on fire

item.wizardrygolems\:ring_charcoal.name=Charcoal Ring
item.wizardrygolems\:ring_charcoal.desc=Fire Golemancy will summon two Furnace Golems. The Golems must be fed with coal to operate. Every additional fuel after the first one increases the golem's lifetime by 10 seconds

item.wizardrygolems\:ring_fire_golem_duration.name=Ring of Fire Golemancy
item.wizardrygolems\:ring_fire_golem_duration.desc=Your Fire Golems have twice as long lifetime

item.wizardrygolems\:ring_flame_golem.name=Sunstone Ring
item.wizardrygolems\:ring_flame_golem.desc=Fire Golemancy will summon a Flame Golem\nFlame Golems wield powerful fire magic and they can imbue their owner's weapon with fire\nRequires a Master Fire Wand

item.wizardrygolems\:charm_fire_golemancy_potency.name=Fire Elemental Heart
item.wizardrygolems\:charm_fire_golemancy_potency.desc=Being near a Fire Golem while holding a Fire Staff will empower the caster's magic\nRequires a Fire Wand

item.wizardrygolems\:charm_ifrit_bottle.name=Sealed Ifrit
item.wizardrygolems\:charm_ifrit_bottle.desc=Your Fire Golems gain a Fireskin effect. Being near a Fire Golem while holding a Fire Wand will grant you fire resistance

item.wizardrygolems\:ring_frostbite.name=Ring of Frostbite
item.wizardrygolems\:ring_frostbite.desc=Your Ice Golemancy golems have 50%% chance to apply Frostbite on hit

item.wizardrygolems\:charm_frost_cloak.name=Frost Cloak
item.wizardrygolems\:charm_frost_cloak.desc=Your Ice Golems gain an Ice Shroud effect. Being near an Ice Golem while holding an Ice Wand will also grant you the effect

item.wizardrygolems\:ring_permanent_golem.name=Ring of the Golemancer
item.wizardrygolems\:ring_permanent_golem.desc=Causes your next golem summoned by any golemancy spell to have unlimited lifetime.\nLimited to one entity at a time\n5 minutes cooldown

item.wizardrygolems\:ring_snow_golem.name=Snowbound Ring
item.wizardrygolems\:ring_snow_golem.desc=Ice Golemancy summons 5 small snow golems
#\nNearby snow blocks can allow summoning more, up to 8

item.wizardrygolems\:ring_winter_golem.name=Glacier Gem Ring
item.wizardrygolems\:ring_winter_golem.desc=Ice Golemancy will summon a Winter Golem\nWinter Golems are powerful creatures of ice magic that can imbue their owner's weapon with the power of ice

item.wizardrygolems\:ring_lodestone_golem.name=Ring of Ferromancy
item.wizardrygolems\:ring_lodestone_golem.desc=Lightning Golemancy summons a Lodestone Golem, equipped with a ranged attack and the ability to manipulate magnetic forces, attracting or repelling nearby entities. Sneak-casting determines the polarity

item.wizardrygolems\:head_maelstrom_golem.name=Mask of Maelstrom
item.wizardrygolems\:head_maelstrom_golem.desc=Lightning Golemancy conjures a Maelstrom Golem, armed with the power of lightning magic\nRequires a Master Lightning Wand.

item.wizardrygolems\:charm_static_aura.name=Cloak of Static Aura
item.wizardrygolems\:charm_static_aura.desc=Your Lightning Golems gain the Static Aura effect. Being near a Lightning Golem while holding a Lightning Wand will also grant you the effect

item.wizardrygolems\:ring_spark_golem.name=Ring of Keraunus
item.wizardrygolems\:ring_spark_golem.desc=Lightning Golemancy summons a Spark Golem. Spark Golems deal magic damage that bypasses mundane armor and exhibit high resistance to physical attacks, albeit they are vulnerable to magic

item.wizardrygolems\:ring_electric_scatter.name=Electric Scatter-Ring
item.wizardrygolems\:ring_electric_scatter.desc=Lightning Golemancy summons 5 small Thunderstone Golems if no other golem-type rings are active. All golems leave behind a trail of lingering electricity.

item.wizardrygolems\:amulet_broken_ice.name=Broken Ice Crystal Amulet
item.wizardrygolems\:amulet_broken_ice.desc=Ice Golemancy golems have 50%% chance to shatter upon death

item.wizardrygolems\:amulet_jagged_sapphire.name=Jagged Sapphire Amulet
item.wizardrygolems\:amulet_jagged_sapphire.desc=Ice Golemancy golems have 15%% chance to cast Ice Spikes under their target with each attack

item.wizardrygolems\:charm_frozen_mark.name=Mark of Frozen Domain
item.wizardrygolems\:charm_frozen_mark.desc=Ice Golemancy golems spawn ice sigils when they are killed

item.wizardrygolems\:charm_living_snow.name=Bottle of Living Snow
item.wizardrygolems\:charm_living_snow.desc=This bottle contains Living Snow that can be placed. Living Snow summons allied Snow Golems if enemies are nearby. The bottle can be recharged at an Arcane Workbench

